You may do a dramatic reading of the following: "I was reimbursed by @Influenster and @<brand> for this product in exchange for my honest review." You must let enough time lapse to read prompt. You should also write that you received the product(s) for free from Influenster and brand> in the first 125 characters of the description. You may copy the sentence above into the beginning of your description.
External Reviews (with no free product sample check box)
Be sure to disclose in your review that you received the product free for testing purposes. It's important others know you received it complimentary, but do give your honest opinion-- the good, the bad and the lovely! If you can't tick a checkbox, this disclosure should be made at the top of the review to ensure that if the review is ever truncated, the full disclosure is viewable.
Not sure how long your disclosure should be? Get inspiration or go ahead and copy your disclosure here!
Disclosures we love and their length (brand name variable):
VoxBox Campaign
This is a product I received for free from @Influenster and @<brand> for my honest review.
(91 characters)
I received this product courtesy of @Influenster and @<brand> in exchange for my honest review.
(95 characters)
I received this complimentary product from @Influnenster and @<brand> in exchange for an honest review.
(104 characters)
Thanks @Influenster and @<brand> for the complementary product and the chance to share my honest thoughts about it!
(115 characters)
Digital Campaign
I was reimbursed by @Influenster and @<brand> for this product in exchange for my honest review.
(97 characters)
I receieved cash back in exchange for my honest review of this product, thanks @Influenster and @<brand>!
(105 characters)
I received cash back from @Influenster and @<brand> for trying this product and sharing my honest review.
(106 characters)
I tried this product and got Cash Back courtesy of @Influenster and @<brand> and now I'm going to share my honest review!
(121 characters)
Want more? We even have a nifty widget you can include on your blog so you can wear your status as an Influenster with pride!
*Remember: If you're unsure on how to disclose, you can always look for the Influenster VoxFox. He's your helpful disclaimer guide to staying in the clear!
Happy Posting!
